Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.libraries.functions

Interface Summary
Function Determines a result based on a number of arguments.
FunctionArgument The argument of a function.
FunctionFactory Creates a function.
 

Class Summary
ConstantFunctionArgument A function argument with a constant value.
FunctionArgumentInformation Provides information about a function argument.
FunctionInformation Gives information on a function.
StaticMethodInvokingFunction A function that invokes a static method.
StaticMethodInvokingFunctionFactory A function factory that creates a function that invokes a static method.
 

Exception Summary
FunctionException Thrown by function factories when a function can't be created and by functions when they can't be called.
